{"hec2a8103g3d80g43a8g988fg67b5e7aa2393": ["Watcha standing 'ere all dry fer? C'mere, have a drink!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "e336d328-ed9d-234c-0d63-805e9086c71c"], "h13d9caa0g65d5g4a6fgbcc1g6613fb3ff0a6": ["What should we toast to, eh?", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "ed3d4725-6a80-85cc-43d8-038210754b87"], "h10131816g424cg4c71gbb6bg763880fbe833": ["It's your party - celebrate it however you like.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "77b3d022-4d0e-d030-94f9-c5a47d5c7da4"], "h84278fd8gc468g4bd8g94ffg03c03d91ea65": ["Ha! I'll show ya how it's done.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "fd9a2439-5aaa-e073-9974-f7fc5f899431"], "h040aa39eg7450g499dg883bg7d54efbb233b": ["A toast! To our victory!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "63e32add-b3b9-d2ab-9a81-83bff7707e24"], "haad37fa8gd430g4320g9abagf48a59396710": ["To tha' duke's face when we gave 'im to the drow!", "10a00987-1dbe-4540-aa34-e96976c7bac0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "7ac7c289-fec5-4031-d591-6ce56cc82bd9"], "h25759303g6202g4e93g8d7fg073e328c6cf6": ["To findin' those looters and crushin' 'em!", "f3f416d1-b946-4019-95ba-7053f63dd776", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "ba3dae54-8d0e-4548-5b08-59fcc16363c1"], "h803ef8cfg81ffg4392g97c9g7614a171751b": ["Now you!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "c6b17b52-dea2-8d74-bd49-13d9775181c7"], "hfb1d00d1ga434g4f36gbeedg36583ce88857": ["*You raise your glass and shout...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "b7175e04-7134-916a-963c-3175bc1d0909"], "hb68ba558g1d05g4f43ga562g2a8f2c98b8a6": ["To me!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "e4dd815a-7e3b-748d-34d9-a9d340f019ad"], "h615c36d3g6d53g46e4gba78gbf78de994804": ["Ehh...", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "82d411dc-a9b5-1f3a-8b09-e0c9f61f04d3"], "h6909df20g083dg475cga099gff4ea15077e7": ["Go on, drink up!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f434f9bf-1fbd-ed83-6ef6-14fea56392f7"], "heebe0723gc407g4254gbdefg3f7b26168fb3": ["<i>Spill the beer, then pretend to drink from the empty cup.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "cf0a02b0-1dc2-0b69-6713-888fbc08b4d5"], "h73fee61dge327g4712gba66gd8d682ba1c48": ["That's it - down the hatch.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "0523e87a-befe-223f-a0c8-26e7adf7828f"], "h04a60467g0e1cg4330gba7eg55ad7a8f8159": ["Hey! That's our beer you're wastin'! Ain't good enough for ya?", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "49ecbaf1-2b98-4fdb-50dd-f80a70e42444"], "h8c421cc6gf466g4b8egbae7gb44ec897f228": ["You think there's somethin' wrong with it?", "f3f416d1-b946-4019-95ba-7053f63dd776", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "686edf41-4d8c-01a4-04fe-3cba48a2e6e2"], "h48d3bf1bgc0b7g4ff7g966bgaf42c2435b70": ["I told ya we shouln't be drinkin' the foam. It ain't right.", "10a00987-1dbe-4540-aa34-e96976c7bac0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "585822dd-59d5-4b27-ce70-b358716f4f93"], "h807a6af4ge7d9g4fa1g8c77gddeba0b29204": ["Wait, 'ave ya been tamperin' with our beer? That what ye've been standin' 'round 'ere for?", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "46018c8f-4495-450f-291a-25071f37e05f"], "hc3babc64g46b5g4f94gb024g04ce73ad4652": ["Don't be stupid. You might be able to drink all day - the Absolute needs me sober.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "c78000b1-5814-1473-4a7d-0505b01b7906"], "h4d09bfbfg3793g4990g8e16g6c046671e342": ["Hah! You drew the short end of the stick, didn't ya? I'd say it's clear who the Absolute favours.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "4dea28f6-3698-645d-4819-019588f67536"], "h4643965ag75e2g47b6gb32dgff63d7d553af": ["<i>Drink quickly to squash their suspicions.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "709cecc8-044d-7f6c-51e3-bf9cf5aadb64"], "h7aeaea07g548ag416cg8014g55ca611857d9": ["*Besides a slight tingle, your stomach doesn't react to the poison.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "23c06ded-d6a3-596b-0fd0-ea0c1e640534"], "hf088dedcg0ccbg47c3g9467g9dab1410289a": ["Hah! Guess you tieflings can't help but look suspicious. Now get outta my way - I need another drink!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "c8cbee23-3858-87cf-091c-c7cc7b7640c1"], "heca69055gcb0fg4d18gbf3bg4abdab07e2d1": ["Guess you can't help but look suspicious, without a nose and all. Now get outta my way - I need another drink!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "c8cbee23-3858-87cf-091c-c7cc7b7640c1"], "hf24471ffg9e38g4bd1g8197gb22081ca4622": ["You looked real suspicious for a bit. Now get outta my way - I need another drink!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "c8cbee23-3858-87cf-091c-c7cc7b7640c1"], "hf93975cbge938g4d69gb556gcdad2eee0c49": ["*The poison burns your throat, but the goblin relaxes.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "53b3c244-2ec8-59d9-d4f0-d23d4857f908"], "h5cb9044ag398fg4940g9036g12bf2e02b31d": ["You caught me. It's poisoned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "523f9de2-b5b6-d6a7-abde-3a107601ea51"], "h5de59bf4gbecag4380g9bf6g9f97e6bc49ed": ["I shoulda known! Get 'er!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "6ce69873-ea1e-627a-c9a5-328dd91c6519"], "he219b65ag0a7fg470ag9b8dg281fe1d8ea1b": ["I shoulda known! Get 'im!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "6ce69873-ea1e-627a-c9a5-328dd91c6519"], "hed244d86gd1b7g4919gb0b9gddc0e10fea16": ["Aw, c'mon. I've already had a few cups... can barely see straight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "bb65c282-e260-4b3d-2dea-38db89828a4d"], "h86d74813g9c9fg45d4g8d78gbdb857f42478": ["Well, watch it - we worked hard for that beer!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "b5e3c91a-c728-c4f0-6c66-913fe6addcca"], "had67c32fgedc8g4cfeg9f0eg779c25976f25": ["Now get outta my way - I need another drink!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "ef3e887d-b59d-10d2-2243-05f760fc5e7b"], "h26dea919gbc58g4759gb7b3gf417b9a55eaa": ["Right, you think I believe that? Lemme show ya how we handle liars 'round here.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "5adbcc43-8b37-1343-16f6-8e4c55bc8ac5"], "hf284f0e3g0911g43dbgb161g4f1ea7eb8a33": ["I was checking none of you idiots had spilled anything foul in there.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "d4a54e76-3e10-9924-f502-fe03f666d604"], "haf4fd01fg12f1g42bega014g4d5cd92db082": ["Yer... what - 'course we didn't!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "dd8bfbfe-4b6d-1bde-e129-377184c3127a"], "he22ef2d9g3369g438eg84a4ge54b75be1309": ["Anyway. 'S good beer, so don't waste it. Now get outta my way - I need another drink!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "d2efd7e5-b8fc-00a3-012f-b0f6e993f35a"], "hc7b6edb5g8875g4f4cg8b01gcb73b1b95dad": ["Yer... what... yer lyin', ain'tcha? Lemme show ya how we handle liars 'round here.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "2adc6448-60bc-3c54-06eb-9007f5938dc6"], "h0a415d88g76b4g4646gad8agfd91853fd91d": ["<i>Read her mind.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "63215ee9-13da-2ac7-efbe-5392c8558ecb"], "he58ebdc8g9e04g4473g9faagfb5d3f4aef22": ["<i>Wastin' beer just like that drow True Soul. Said she needed a clear head for Absolute business. Bah!</i>", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "2bb83587-1834-dc52-7a00-c1e0d3a825ea"], "h01a4b0a0g8199g4bdeg8bbbge25200590d54": ["Hey! Whatcha doin'? I knew there was something off 'bout you! Get 'er!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "49496612-ceb3-9565-0405-e97c8e8fb1a2"], "hb3877220g014bg4108gb837g38ac251cc3c6": ["Hey! Whatcha doin'? I knew there was something off 'bout you! Get 'im!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "49496612-ceb3-9565-0405-e97c8e8fb1a2"], "h4f8f45f6g78fag489eg8a7dgc468ddc3b055": ["After you! I shouldn't drink before the host.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "8524307c-72d5-3fb6-871b-4ec5b3a36ded"], "h38be4301g518dg4e1agacceg94baa5721679": ["Why not? Wait, 'ave ya been tamperin' wif our beer? That what ye've been standin' 'round 'ere for?", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "e2a0d5bb-f5e5-4c5b-5a7e-a5f063f80292"], "h0c643420g909eg4b79g80efgbefac09a918a": ["<i>Down the beer.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "d3160ab9-ed79-f59f-63b0-cd43bb67943a"], "hf9383e80gf595g4b82ga4bdge0ce42e1994a": ["*The poison burns your throat, but the goblins follow your lead.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "ab209e34-b7d4-8bcc-fdfa-a318bae9c593"], "h98d51a01gb096g4b07gbfc4gc76ecf21bea6": ["I'm simply being a good guest, that's all.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "fe4eeea9-e8d5-f8fe-f43b-15dc00d4c59c"], "hb0c2ab10g8b88g43e7ga41eg0acc68dbd296": ["That's how you end up dry, mate - not that I'm complainin'! ", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "4222a3e3-b4d9-df4b-3bfb-7055940fb950"], "h27be6c32gdf51g46c4gb176g383a702aecef": ["<i>Perform a party trick.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "88c63700-0aa3-d92d-65c1-ba5530dcfb69"], "hb9f5fbafg4f56g480cgb9cfgfae248b025d5": ["Bravo!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "061b5e28-b64f-80c5-0497-25b50291c3d4"], "haedd61cfg5cc7g49b6g84a4g822977378c32": ["Amateur!", "f3f416d1-b946-4019-95ba-7053f63dd776", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "2312e328-3d50-4b2a-ff23-3325b807bd9d"], "h4e8d7471g0444g45dfgacdbg595095cf33f2": ["Amateur!", "10a00987-1dbe-4540-aa34-e96976c7bac0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "549106e7-afc8-64b8-f887-3518b2fbf308"], "hc57f4ecbg2455g47c5g88d1gd849e234f683": ["To the Absolute!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "a0406cb5-0312-dd8a-e4c9-b879535532fc"], "h69d57fb1g9df9g4fcfg8ee0g24f650975e8d": ["To Tyr, maimed and mighty!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "hd037d589g103cg4e1bg88d5g7d87cf8ec217": ["To Sel\u00fbne, who lights the way!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "hd744e59eg9737g4b59g8298g0a7cf87a0ca8": ["To Ilmater, who always endures!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "h48595184g6762g4f42g91feg61299617bc0d": ["To Mystra, mother of the Weave!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "h09a34e05gdbf1g4c0aga798gd32528249d76": ["To Helm, ever-vigilant!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "hf4b11da5gd4bbg4a75gaa0eg69dae61cddff": ["To Kelemvor, who judges us all!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "h1b7a85a4g6a45g40ddga12ag949ca94422d2": ["To Oghma, father of knowledge!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "hd370a7ccg119eg4078g98b1gfdddde6b6822": ["To Tempus, who crushes his foes!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "h9551ef85g066fg4c31gb5d3g1364e4973088": ["To Shar, mistress of the night!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "h712119ecgb61ag4039gba2dgf907f4b71e2e": ["To Bhaal, who bleeds the world dry!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "haa2ddf10gf4ffg499ega99fga323bb45ef6f": ["To Bane, rightful ruler!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "hd7c4798eg355fg415fgab3bgd5ecd9d570df": ["To Myrkul, lord of bones!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f29720cb-f396-5e5a-5900-5ac9cee1fea4"], "h132877f3g6f23g4191g99a1g1e37b89057a5": ["*The goblins blink at you in confusion.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "3cb82d93-e02d-f98d-1825-b6b30940a5f2"], "ha08741aaga8acg470eg8060gb4aac2c3bf73": ["To... our health?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "b934a8c9-5d1e-b8f0-0c8a-951c6e3f14e3"], "h2d58534egd89dg4f6bg8322gf7b25c94f914": ["To drinking 'til we die!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "bdd3ac3a-a6f8-2c16-ad88-2627d547f3a2"], "haf099cf0ga8d3g4cfaga92bg9ebb8e7edf11": ["May I bed each and every one of you before the sun sets!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "d5c37eb0-77bd-0bb4-d115-0cad76c8e204"], "hbc4201beg1ee3g42e4gbff7gbf7cc0633715": ["Ya can always take a bite out of me!", "1fe911f8-c9c9-4405-83fa-d343d59c7be9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "cee93b9a-d205-decd-37d0-7dee2946b64c"], "h7e1d2092gddd7g4b59gb86eg39db05c69c96": ["I'm glad you asked. Tell everyone to gather round...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "7539a969-c439-7945-2f0b-bba4c7fa67fc"], "h10206a50g2d35g487eg86abg3efb06c1159c": ["Guys! This 'un's givin' us a toast!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "b1cf607a-d686-4b98-3d64-d803074f3296"], "h7f7458e3gcbeeg4d53ga090gb46b6ce490d4": ["I'll pass. Need a clear head for now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "9e3fd3d6-e70e-ca07-5262-659a0fca765f"], "ha9401848gb79cg48acgb764g87b24a968310": ["Oh, go away! You elves think you're all special.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "61dcc621-ad62-6665-cfc5-6836bb2a9106"], "hd436e3e9gef23g450fg9d9egcddf13a3ea6e": ["Oh, go away! You humans think you're all special.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "61dcc621-ad62-6665-cfc5-6836bb2a9106"], "h17f40aa3ga29cg476dgb435g5150c64d63c4": ["Oh, go away!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "61dcc621-ad62-6665-cfc5-6836bb2a9106"], "hf7265f5bg7d6cg4cb1gb450g6f40975ca04a": ["Party pooper. An' I thought dwarves knew how t' drink.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f4c1c872-61cd-8cb8-faee-40be1ed4f437"], "h80e57759ga0b9g4ca1gbae7gf18bb432d493": ["Party pooper. An' I thought 'alflings were s'posed to be nice.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f4c1c872-61cd-8cb8-faee-40be1ed4f437"], "h7eb1155dg4f64g43c5ga37bg3d228954cb66": ["Party pooper. Last time I give one of you ants a drink.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f4c1c872-61cd-8cb8-faee-40be1ed4f437"], "h63918d86g26b7g4a4bgadc5g9d8b4c7daf22": ["Party pooper. Last time I give one of ya overgrown beasts a drink.", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "f4c1c872-61cd-8cb8-faee-40be1ed4f437"], "h57576622g735dg4889gbe20ga636c522e373": ["Hey! That's our beer you're wastin'! Shove off!", "e63401de-04ea-40b6-a988-b2f90a90f748", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinToast.html", "917155e7-02e2-3e8c-6c8e-f510f662c9f4"]}